\mt1 A Message from the Translator
\p Welcome to the all-new, 2026 release of the English Majority Text Version of the New Testament, released here once again as The Annotated EMTV New Testament.
\q1 “Every word of God is pure;
\li1 1. How to have peace with God.
\li1 2. How to stand before Him on Judgment Day, and to be accepted in the Beloved.
